  <p>
    If you are hooked by the history and want to paddle the same river Dionisio did, <a href="/en/premium-booking/">pick a date in the calendar</a>. And if you coincide with the <a href="/en/international-sella-descent/">Saturday of the International Descent</a>, stay at least to watch it — it is the real way to understand why this river became what it is.
  </p>
